09|website=Times Higher Education (THE)|language=en|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.uaar.edu.pk/about-us.php?content_id=100|title=About us {{!}} PMAS-Arid Agriculture University Rawalpindi|website=www.uaar.edu.pk|access-date=2020-04-10}}</ref>\n\n== Academic Programs ==\nFollowing academic programs are offered at Barani Institute of Sciences:<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://topschools.pk/|title=Top Colleges and Universities in Pakistan|website=TopSchools|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n=== '''Management Sciences''' ===\n\n# Bachelor of Business Administration<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://baraniinstitute.edu.pk/course/bba-hons/|title=BBA Hons admission 2019 {{!}} Barani Institute of Sciences Burewala & Sahiwal|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n=== '''Social Sciences''' ===\n\n# Bachelor of Science in Economics<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://baraniinstitute.edu.pk/course/bs-economics/|title=BS Economics admission 2019 {{!}} Barani Institute of Sciences Burewala & Sahiwal|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n# Master of Sciences in Economics<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://baraniinstitute.edu.pk/course/m-sc-economics/|title=M.Sc Economics admission 2019 {{!}} Barani Institute of Sciences Burewala & Sahiwal|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n\n=== '''Computer Sciences''' ===\n\n# Bachelor of Science in Computer Science<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://baraniinstitute.edu.pk/course/bs-computer-science/|title=BSCS Admissions 2019 {{!}} Barani Institute of Sciences Burewala & Sahiwal|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n# Bachelor of Science in Information Technology<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://baraniinstitute.edu.pk/course/bs-information-technology/|title=BSIT Admissions 2019 {{!}} Barani Institute of Sciences Burewala & Sahiwal|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-13}}</ref>\n# Master of Computer Science<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://baraniinstitute.edu.pk/course/master-in-computer-science/|title=MCS Admissions 2019